  "text": "Clear advantages of DNAzyme compared to other RNA-targeting agents include its ease of chemical synthesis, good stability and high catalytic turnover [CITATION_1] . Recently, a clinical trial demonstrated the antitumor and radiosensitizing effects of DZ1 [CITATION_2] . Here, we demonstrated HIF-1/VEGF activation induced by LMP1 in NPC cells occurs through JNKs /c-Jun -dependent pathways, which resulted in decreased angiogenesis and increased radiosensitivity in NPC cells.",
